1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 14=

3
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:48,880
Shaoyuan,

4
00:00:49,760 --> 00:00:52,280
have I not treated you well enough?

5
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:55,079
Whatever you want,

6
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:56,760
I can give it to you.

7
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,040
Gu Nianchi,

8
00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:00,240
from the moment you approached me,

9
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,960
wasn't your plan
to make me your scapegoat?

10
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:08,760
I'm only taking back
what rightfully belongs to me.

11
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:15,280
But you're my own little brother.

12
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,440
When I am in trouble,
you should help me.

13
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:21,480
Instead, you're trying to replace me.

14
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:24,960
Is that really right?

15
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:28,920
The one who replaced someone was you.

16
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,320
What you still don't know

17
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:34,719
is that because of you,
I was separated from the person

18
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:37,360
I loved most for three whole years.

19
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,480
The person you loved most?

20
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:45,800
Are you bringing up old history with me?

21
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:49,800
That was all years ago, wasn't it?

22
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,200
Is there really any need
to mention it again?

23
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,000
Oh, right.

24
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,720
Didn't you like your sister in law?

25
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:57,600
I can give her to you too.

26
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,120
And besides,

27
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,480
however much money you want,

28
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,400
I can give it to you.

29
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,560
Enough.

30
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,760
Back then, I went off to war
to earn money for the family,

31
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:11,120
and left you at home to care for Mother.

32
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,320
But what happened in the end?

33
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,799
When I returned with military honors,

34
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:18,760
I found Mother already dead
from illness at home,

35
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:20,720
and you had vanished without a trace.

36
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,520
You stole my identity,

37
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,280
and slaughtered the entire village

38
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:28,799
just to keep the villagers
from exposing you.

39
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,440
So many innocent lives.

40
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,320
Do you really feel

41
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:36,960
no guilt at all?

42
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:40,760
Shaoyan.

43
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,520
Guilt?

44
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,800
Shaoyuan,

45
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:01,520
only the weak use morality
to judge the strong.

46
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,000
And the strong

47
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,760
can keep the weak

48
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,720
beneath their feet forever.

49
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:14,160
Gu Shaoyan!

50
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,400
What did you call me?

51
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,139
I called you Gu Shaoyan!

52
00:03:18,140 --> 00:03:19,079
My name is Gu Nianchi,

53
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,159
not Gu Shaoyan!

54
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:22,159
Did you hear me clearly?
My name is Gu Nianchi!

55
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,080
Men!

56
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,280
Seize him!

57
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,160
What are you doing?

58
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,440
I said,

59
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,200
seize him!

60
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,280
What's this?

61
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:01,400
You've been hiding this thing

62
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,360
inside the opera house.

63
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,680
I found it.

64
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,320
Back when you took my place,

65
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:14,840
I originally thought that if you could
become a good Commander,

66
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,560
and protect the people,

67
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:19,600
I would willingly
hand this position over to you.

68
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,720
But every single thing you've done

69
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:26,319
has filled people

70
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:28,120
with outrage and hatred.

71
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,640
So,

72
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,160
starting today,

73
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:36,400
I am the Commander of Yancheng.

74
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,120
Take him back to
the Commander's Residence.

75
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,560
Yes.

76
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,240
Yunqiu.

77
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:05,640
Where's Yunqiu?

78
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,200
Yunqiu?

79
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,400
Madam.

80
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,840
Oh, Madam,

81
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,360
I haven't seen her.

82
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,440
Yunqiu!

83
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,160
Yunqiu!

84
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,280
Yunqiu!

85
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,400
Yunqiu!

86
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,170
Yunqiu!

87
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,210
Yunqiu!

88
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:46,540
Yunqiu!

89
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,680
(We were separated for three years.)

90
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:58,030
(When we met again,)

91
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,760
(I thought you were my enemy.)

92
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:04,440
(And you thought I was Xue Wan,
the eldest daughter of the Xue family.)

93
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:07,080
(Fate truly loves to toy with people.)

94
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,720
Find Madam for me, no matter what.

95
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:16,800
Yes.

96
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:28,120
(Did you recognize me long ago?)

97
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:31,360
(While I kept pushing you
away again and again.)

98
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:34,080
(Have I already broken your heart?)

99
00:06:34,410 --> 00:06:40,080
♪Entangled through lifetimes,
drawn into chaos and schemes♪

100
00:06:40,650 --> 00:06:43,590
♪Your silhouette♪

101
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:45,519
Have you seen a woman about this tall?

102
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:47,080
No, no.

103
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:53,410
♪Love and longing
traced through countless lifetimes♪

104
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,360
Have you seen this person?

105
00:06:56,690 --> 00:06:59,500
♪Right and wrong no longer clear♪

106
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:01,199
♪The world becomes a prison♪

107
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,880
A woman about this tall.
Have you seen her?

108
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,760
No.

109
00:07:06,490 --> 00:07:08,499
♪This heart and love slowly fade away♪

110
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:10,199
You three, come with me over there.

111
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,200
Yes.

112
00:07:12,740 --> 00:07:14,509
♪Crossing through
the barriers of dreams♪

113
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:15,939
♪Burning away all my devotion♪

114
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:18,720
♪Etching our promises
into each other's hearts♪

115
00:07:19,090 --> 00:07:22,350
♪If the years
are left to waste for too long♪

116
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,870
♪How can love remain so calm?♪

117
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,229
Yunqiu!

118
00:07:27,230 --> 00:07:28,739
♪Nothing more than an excuse♪

119
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:32,210
♪Where in time did my heart belong?♪

120
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:33,880
Yunqiu!

121
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:38,089
♪I still long to hold you once again♪

122
00:07:38,090 --> 00:07:39,599
♪When love runs deep♪

123
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,199
Yunqiu!

124
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,459
♪Why fear growing old together?♪

125
00:07:41,460 --> 00:07:46,800
♪Let the frost wither
the greenery beyond the window♪

126
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,960
Were you looking for me?

127
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,560
Gu Nianchi.

128
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:19,500
♪Fates intertwined,
right and wrong no longer clear♪

129
00:08:19,590 --> 00:08:21,750
♪The world becomes a prison♪

130
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,720
Zhuang Yunqiu.

131
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,879
♪This heart and love slowly fade away♪

132
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:32,110
♪What kind of ending
will this fate bring?♪

133
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:34,449
♪Crossing through
the barriers of dreams♪

134
00:08:34,450 --> 00:08:36,039
♪Burning away all my devotion♪

135
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:38,750
♪Etching our promises
into each other's hearts♪

136
00:08:39,170 --> 00:08:42,409
♪If the years are left
to waste for too long♪

137
00:08:42,410 --> 00:08:45,619
♪How can love remain so calm?♪

138
00:08:45,620 --> 00:08:48,849
♪So called blame,
nothing more than an excuse♪

139
00:08:48,850 --> 00:08:51,899
♪Where in time did my heart belong?♪

140
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:55,219
♪Even if time has given up on us♪

141
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:58,399
♪I still long to hold you once again♪

142
00:08:58,400 --> 00:09:01,489
♪When love runs deep,
why fear growing old together?♪

143
00:09:01,490 --> 00:09:03,779
♪Let the frost wither
the greenery beyond the window♪

144
00:09:03,780 --> 00:09:05,080
What's your name?

145
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:07,640
My name is Zhuang Yunqiu.

146
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,800
What about you?

147
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,800
My name is Gu Nianchi.

148
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:14,499
♪Nothing more than an excuse♪

149
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:17,649
♪Where in time did my heart belong?♪

150
00:09:17,650 --> 00:09:20,849
♪Even if time has given up on us♪

151
00:09:20,850 --> 00:09:23,979
♪I still long to hold you once again♪

152
00:09:23,980 --> 00:09:27,099
♪When love runs deep,
why fear growing old together?♪

153
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:32,810
♪Let the frost wither
the greenery beyond the window♪

154
00:09:36,940 --> 00:09:42,340
♪Love quietly hides within the wind♪

155
00:09:42,420 --> 00:09:47,480
♪Falling into your smile before my eyes♪

156
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,280
What are you trying to do?

157
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:54,880
What you have always wanted to do to me.

158
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,160
When did I ever?

159
00:09:59,000 --> 00:09:59,979
Then let me do it instead.

160
00:09:59,980 --> 00:10:05,740
♪Love is so strange,
the way it entangles me♪

161
00:10:06,020 --> 00:10:11,599
♪I still haven't awakened,
though I know I shouldn't♪

162
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,770
Commander.

163
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,200
Remember this.

164
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,520
My name is Lu Shaoyuan.

165
00:10:20,490 --> 00:10:22,950
♪Joy and pleasure♪

166
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:29,250
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

167
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:35,880
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

168
00:10:36,380 --> 00:10:39,960
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

169
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:43,310
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

170
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:48,600
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

171
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:54,910
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

172
00:10:55,970 --> 00:11:01,570
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

173
00:11:02,110 --> 00:11:05,490
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

174
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:08,689
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

175
00:11:08,690 --> 00:11:13,829
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

176
00:11:13,830 --> 00:11:18,149
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

177
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:20,729
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

178
00:11:20,730 --> 00:11:23,009
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

179
00:11:23,010 --> 00:11:26,559
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

180
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:31,089
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

181
00:11:31,090 --> 00:11:33,620
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

182
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,709
♪Still I walk into♪

183
00:11:35,710 --> 00:11:39,309
♪The trap you set without regret♪

184
00:11:39,310 --> 00:11:43,359
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

185
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:45,939
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

186
00:11:45,940 --> 00:11:48,099
♪A stand in can never cross♪

187
00:11:48,100 --> 00:11:51,539
♪The shortest distance between us♪

188
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:56,510
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

189
00:11:56,670 --> 00:12:01,340
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

190
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,689
♪A substitute♪

191
00:12:05,690 --> 00:12:10,690
♪Needs no reason♪

